            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            现实即弯路的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 23 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5400561">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5400561/" class="title-link">《现实即弯路》之后我为什么写诗</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5400561"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/47613525/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u47613525-22.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/47613525/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">诗人邹波</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-04-23"
      class="main-meta">2012-04-23 09:22:47</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5400561_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  邹波  我继续在破晓的时光里修改我的诗，我的生活也继续简化，它吸干了我几乎所有垃圾时间（这就像古典音乐响起，匡正了一切发呆的时光），即使我必须深深浅浅若有若无地同外部世界交谈着，并奢望保持着友谊，我也想起人们评价爱伦•坡时所说：“坡从不犯错，即使写出劣诗的...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5400561/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">57有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
